    {
      "id": "Jcp1OkouODQ6tTjXQ1Vgi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 192,
      "y": 208,
      "width": 1304.7154541015625,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1976425088,
      "version": 239,
      "versionNonce": 443923840,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776072964355,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Facade Design Pattern :- provides a simplified, unified interface to a set of complex subsystem\nIt hides the complexity of the system and expose only what is necessary to users.\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Facade Design Pattern :- provides a simplified, unified interface to a set of complex subsystem\nIt hides the complexity of the system and expose only what is necessary to users.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "w5O-Xh73ArlnEWNHhmVGB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 313,
      "y": 314,
      "width": 1117.9393310546875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1773730432,
      "version": 420,
      "versionNonce": 1629629824,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "Ylm3rPEQutqp3ln9sofc_",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1776072277159,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A class that we introduce for the client so that we can hide the complexity of system. \nFacade class is like Gateway that we provide to client so that client can just talk to facade and facade handles \nall the complex work for client, It decouples with client, also helps to implement \nPRINCIPLE OF LEAST KNOWLEDGE\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A class that we introduce for the client so that we can hide the complexity of system. \nFacade class is like Gateway that we provide to client so that client can just talk to facade and facade handles \nall the complex work for client, It decouples with client, also helps to implement \nPRINCIPLE OF LEAST KNOWLEDGE\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
