      "text": "Has a",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "_UlCkpDHUPY1DnykkZ9TO",
      "originalText": "Has a",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CldtvUwifYNehQfmhtqys",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1133,
      "y": 653,
      "width": 467.0196533203125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ac",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 232590720,
      "version": 114,
      "versionNonce": 2008178048,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776072365532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Facade has all the internal config to wokr with \nsubsystem hiding the complexity from client",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Facade has all the internal config to wokr with \nsubsystem hiding the complexity from client",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "h_gnNdTscxxhJNXkhqg6I",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 302,
      "y": 1407,
      "width": 1291.8994140625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ae",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 222108288,
      "version": 460,
      "versionNonce": 1699597696,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776072573083,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Principle of Least Knowldege:- Talk only to your immediate friends only, A->B->C then A can only call the methods of B, A will never \ncall the methods of C directly, If A want to call the methods of C then A will call it throght the B and B has to have written the \nmethods to handle Cs methods. \nWe make strict interaction to make it loosely coupled design!!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Principle of Least Knowldege:- Talk only to your immediate friends only, A->B->C then A can only call the methods of B, A will never \ncall the methods of C directly, If A want to call the methods of C then A will call it throght the B and B has to have written the \nmethods to handle Cs methods. \nWe make strict interaction to make it loosely coupled design!!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VJrZc0guFb6TnRERKLbiU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 309,
      "y": 1577,
      "width": 574.5877075195312,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ah",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 166915456,
      "version": 62,
      "versionNonce": 1607052672,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776072604212,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Principle of Least Knowledge Guidelines :- ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Principle of Least Knowledge Guidelines :- ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7go1vVBrUl2Bfh89YLFie",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 305,
      "y": 1637,
      "width": 1155.719482421875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ai",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1651940736,
      "version": 345,
      "versionNonce": 1449388672,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776072725882,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Take any object, now from any method in that object, this principle tells you to invoke only methods that belong to :-\n     - The object itself\n     - The Object passed in as a parameter to the method\n     - Any object that method creates.\n     - Any object with has-a Relationship.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Take any object, now from any method in that object, this principle tells you to invoke only methods that belong to :-\n     - The object itself\n     - The Object passed in as a parameter to the method\n     - Any object that method creates.\n     - Any object with has-a Relationship.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jlue--4Xk3z8l7KUwnbIb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 331,
      "y": 1824,
      "width": 1206.419189453125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ak",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1507216000,
      "version": 207,
      "versionNonce": 468200832,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776073025443,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Facade vs Adapter Design pattern:- the main diffrence is intent. that facade is to hide the complexity while adapter is to \nmake the interaction btw completly diffrent interfaces.",
